 Without Christ, but is still thwarted in his efforts to lose God. He meets Enoch Emery, a young man with "wise blood," who leads him to a mummified holy child, and whose crazy maneuvers are a manifestation of Hazel's existential struggles. This tale of redemption, retribution, false prophets, blindness, blindings, and wisdoms gives us one of the most riveting characters in twentieth-century American fiction.</span></div></div></div></div><div data-testid="genresList" class="BookPageMetadataSection__genres"><div class="ChipList"><ul class="TruncatedItems TruncatedItems--ul"><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--visible"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/fiction" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Fiction</span></a></div></li><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--visible"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/classics" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Classics</span></a></div></li><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--visible"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/southern-gothic" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Southern Gothic</span></a></div></li><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--visible"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/literature" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Literature</span></a></div></li><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--hidden"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/novels" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Novels</span></a></div></li><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--hidden"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/southern" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Southern</span></a></div></li><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--hidden"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/american" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">American</span></a></div></li><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--hidden"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/gothic" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Gothic</span></a></div></li><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--hidden"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/religion" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Religion</span></a></div></li><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--hidden"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/literary-fiction" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Literary Fiction</span></a></div></li><li class="TruncatedItems__item"><div class="Button__container"><button type="button" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">...more</span></button></div></li></ul></div></div><div class="BookDetails"><span class="Text Text__body3"><div class="TruncatedItems TruncatedItems--div"><div class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--visible"><div class="FeaturedDetails"><p data-testid="pagesFormat">256 pages, Paperback</p><p data-testid="publicationInfo">First published January 1, 1952</p></div></div><div class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--hidden"><div class="WorkDetails"><div class="DescListItem"><dt>Original Title</dt><dd><span class="TruncatedItems TruncatedItems--span"><span class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--visible">Wise Blood</span></span></dd></div><div class="DescListIt